01:54:37.840 --> 01:54:40.640
[Guest]: absolutely absolutely I agree with you entirely I mean of course we are losing

01:54:40.640 --> 01:54:45.440
[Guest]: out and on this immense richness I mean how can you be how can who allows you

01:54:45.640 --> 01:54:49.440
[Guest]: why should anyone allow you or not allow you I mean you are a free person you can

01:54:49.640 --> 01:54:53.440
[Guest]: write what you like you know of course this whole hurt sentiments business is

