[Guest]: like chamar and you know using caste names which were just caste names simply

01:55:03.640 --> 01:55:08.440
[Guest]: he's not using them in a derogatory sense but I mean there's this whole Dalit

01:55:08.440 --> 01:55:12.240
[Guest]: movement going on against him that how dare he write how can he write about

01:55:12.440 --> 01:55:16.240
[Guest]: people whom he is a high caste person so why is he writing about these people

