[Guest]: there that person stops growing so she has this thing that she's killed her brother because he

02:43:44.520 --> 02:43:48.120
[Guest]: dies later and then she thinks oh i killed him because i jumped over his body and he stopped

02:43:48.120 --> 02:43:52.760
